description:
This is a 9 minute workout called '10-Minute Guided Meditation: Self-Love | SELF' from the channel SELF.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join Manoj Dias, meditation teacher and co-founder and VP of Open, for a 10-minute guided meditation that prioritizes self-love.
